<plot>Runner takes its audience as close as possible to the mental and physical experience of doing the Great North Run through the moving image. Using material from the race itself and combining this with specially shot sequences of a single runner, it follows the journey of a man, one soul in the flood of 50,000.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?470701</url></doc>
